modName: Feminine Khajiit Textures (Grey Cat and Leopard)
summary: This is a retexture for the Khajiit female, it will make your Khajiit looks more feminine.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-0-1460975822.png[/img][/center][center][size=4][font=Courier New]Please read the [color=#ff0000]sticky posts[/color] for extra information[/font][/size][/center]
[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-0-1460976173.png[/img][/center]
[font=Courier New][size=3][center][i]Ever wanted to play a khajiit race and the only thing that made you change your mind is their looks?, well not anymore!, this mod will make your khajiit looks more like human with sexier appearance, Feminine Khajiit comes with two main variations (Grey Cat and Leopard), including 4 options each:
[/i]
[i][color=#00ffff][b]- Abs:[/b][/color] Now your khajiit will be able to do more than 100 crunches![/i]
[i][color=#00ffff][b]- Normal Nipples:[/b][/color] For your normal taste.[/i]
[i][color=#00ffff][b]- 6 Extra Nipples:[/b][/color] I bet these little khajiit babies are hungry!
[i][color=#00ffff][b]- Furry:[/b][/color] Purrrrrrrrr!![/i][/i][/center]
[/size][/font]

[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-1-1460976173.png[/img][/center][center][youtube]Y7_7k7bwTGA[/youtube] [youtube]onIJpKDcKus[/youtube] [youtube]3ZPgBtLt2vQ[/youtube] [youtube]agzci3pxLHM[/youtube] [youtube]01VLD5lI78Q[/youtube][/center]
[center]Note: Some of these vids featured old versions[/center]
[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-2-1460976172.png[/img][/center][font=Courier New][size=3]
[/size][/font][center][i][font=Courier New][size=3][i][font=Courier New][size=3]- Install normally via NMM.
- If installing manually, [i][font=Courier New][size=3]pick either Grey Cat or Leopard then pick one of chest options, then [/size][/font][/i]you need to place "Textures" folder inside "Data" folder, replace files if prompt,
[/size][/font][/i][color=#ff0000](don't forget to backup your original files).
[/color]
[i][font=Courier New][size=3]- CBBE Version: CBBE body is required for these textures to work properly.[/size][/font][/i]
 [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666]Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-
[/url][/size][/font]
[i][font=Courier New][size=3]- UNP Version: UNP body is required for these textures to work properly.[/size][/font][/i]
[font=Courier New][size=3] [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body

[/url][/size][/font][/i][i][i][font=Courier New][size=3][i][font=Courier New][size=3]- Vanilla Version: This doesn't require anything, you're good to go.[/size][/font][/i][/size][/font][/i][/i][/center][i]
[center]
[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-3-1460976172.png[/img][/center][/i][center][i][font=Courier New][size=3][i]- This mod is compatible with all mods as long as using CBBE body with my CBBE textures or UNP body with my UNP textures.
[/i][i]
[/i]- CBBE version is compatible with [i][font=Courier New][size=3]CHSBHC and [/size][/font][/i]HDT.

[i][font=Courier New][size=3]- For UNP version, this is compatible with UNPB and 7b.
[/size][/font][/i]
[/size][/font][/i][i][font=Courier New][size=3]- Using other khajiit head textures will make the character looks awkward, head's color is gonna be different than body's color, unless you want that.[/size][/font][/i][/center]

[center][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/75078-4-1460976172.png[/img][/center][font=Courier New][size=3][size=3][i]
[center]- [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3330686]Caliente[/url] (Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-).

- [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1379129]Utruiwe[/url] and [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3851195]Nerevar22g[/url] (Leopard texture).
- [url=http://rd.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/35431]Eiries[/url] (Ohmes-Raht).
- [url=https://bethesda.net/]Bethesda[/url] (Skyrim).[/center][/i][/size][/size][/font]

files.changelogHtml:
- Many improvements on the textures (However no more support for 1K)
- Fixed some visible seams
- Furry variation is now available for both Grey Cat and Leopard
- Optimized files compression and sizes
- Included resolution packs in one installation
- Edited NMM installation script to add the new changes
